.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/make-your-last-prayer-witr\/","url_meta":{"origin":28187,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Witr: Make last prayer at night Witr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMake the last of your prayers at night the Witr prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 998, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 751 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36185,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/16\/separating-witr-maghrib\/","url_meta":{"origin":28187,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Witr: Separating raka\u2019at of Witr from previous prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not perform Witr prayer with three cycles, rather perform it with five or seven. Do not make it resemble sunset prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 2429 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Al-Bayhaqi said, \u201cWe\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0